data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious and elegant 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence with a pre-plumbed unfinished basement is a true gem. Offering an expansive 2,535 square feet of living space, this property provides both comfort and versatility for your lifestyle. The large family room is the heart of the house, complete with an electric fireplace that adds warmth and charm. Its open design provides uninterrupted views into the kitchen, making it an ideal space for family gatherings and entertaining. Designed with the chef in mind, the kitchen boasts custom cabinets, luxurious quartz countertops, a beautifully tiled backsplash, and a suite of stainless steel appliances, including a stove, dishwasher, and micro hood. Two walk-in pantries offer ample storage, ensuring you have everything you need at your fingertips. The unfinished basement comes pre-plumbed, providing a blank canvas for your creativity. Customize this space to suit your specific needs and create additional living space, a home gym, or a recreation area. With its open floor plan, abundant space and an unfinished basement that's ready for your personal touch, this home is perfect for those seeking a comfortable and versatile living space. Whether you're a growing family, a professional in need of a home office, or an investor, this property has something to offer everyone.
